  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00236', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-113-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據公路法，下列何者不屬慢車？', '["腳踏自行車", "電動輔助自行車", "電動自行車", "電動三輪車"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06f4ea4edc6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9cdda496d42f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "512", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00237', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-113-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據航業法，以自己之名義，為他人之計算，使船舶運送業運送貨物而受報酬為營業之事業，稱之為：', '["海運承攬運送業", "船務代理業", "船舶運送業", "貨櫃集散站經營業"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06f4ea4edc6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9cdda496d42f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "512", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00238', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-113-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '交通部為辦理全國觀光發展業務，下設何單位？', '["觀光局", "觀光署", "觀光司", "觀光推動委員會"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06f4ea4edc6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9cdda496d42f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "512", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00239', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-113-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '法律依憲法第170條之規定，係指經立法院三讀通過，總統公布施行者，此為形式意義之法律；而其名稱 依中央法規標準法第2條規定，下列何者錯誤？', '["律", "規則", "法", "通則"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06f4ea4edc6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9cdda496d42f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "512", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00240', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-113-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '無縫運輸（Seamlesstransportation）係指整合不同運輸系統之營運方式與實體硬體設施，以提供運輸系統 使用效率，有關無縫運輸之維度下列何者錯誤？', '["資訊無縫", "空間無縫", "時間無縫", "票價無縫"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06f4ea4edc6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9cdda496d42f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "512", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
